insert into "products" ("body_html", "created_at", "handle", "id", "image", "images", "options", "product_type", "published_at", "published_scope", "tags", "template_suffix", "title", "metafields_global_title_tag", "metafields_global_description_tag", "updated_at", "variants", "vendor") values ('Your gear doesnt take excuses - it just takes a beating. As a law enforcement or military professional, you need a flashlight that can stand up to the rigors of active duty. Jetbeams IIM combines brute force, self-defense. The IIM rides comfortably on your belt or in a holster with its integrated clip, and the tail switch allows you to deploy and activate it one-handed. Twist the tail to engage the lockout feature, which will prevent button presses from changing your settings. With your thumb comfortably on the tail, you can deliver a hammer strike to your foes with the crenelated front bezel, or disorient them with the lights strobe mode. Select between four brightness settings to preserve your night vision, reduce your visibility, or light up a distant target. And when you power down, the light remembers your last brightness level, meaning you dont have to waste precious seconds cycling through settings. Dont worry about whether the IIM can withstand the strains of your work environment. It can. Its impact resistant for drops up to 1.5 m, meaning you can drop it from eye level and it wont even hiccup. The IIMs IPX-8 rating means the housing is sealed and waterproof for up to 2 m of submersion. The housing is made from airplane-grade aluminum, renowned for its balance of lightness and durability. Power it up with your choice of two different cells: the high-capacity, rechargeable 186540, or two CR123As.Jetbeam IIMK Flashlight Black

Condition : This item is brand new, unopened and sealed in its original factory box.
